original_title: Confessions of a Phish: Clock Pieoe
overview: Is Ohio the fish or the phisher? The film’s sexual metaphor extends to artists, who use their own experiences as material for their work, becoming both fish and fisher, harvester and harvested. Ohio’s deeply intimate documentary footage and audio recordings serve as the raw material for her exploration of class, art, and the performance of heterosexuality.
title: Confessions of a Phish: Clock Pieoe
